# Append-only sidecar logs are NDJSON (one JSON object per line) so concurrent
# appends from parallel feature worktrees merge losslessly. union-merge is only
# safe on line-oriented files — see skills/shared/mode2-codex-lane.md §9.
# Pointwise/overwritten JSON (last-review, last-session, routing) get NO union.
.atomic-skills/status/dispatch-log.json merge=union
# Append-only markdown ledgers (date-keyed / append-list rows are line-independent)
# also union losslessly — wired so N-worktree consolidation never hand-merges them
# (the dominant repeated-conflict tail in the 7-plan consolidation). The
# `project consolidate` driver carries the same union as a fallback for trees
# where this attribute is not yet active.
.atomic-skills/reviews/INDEX.md merge=union
.atomic-skills/projects/*/ideas.md merge=union
scripts/emit-consumer-state.js text
